fields.text: My story is a lot like yours, only more interesting 'cause it involves robots.
fields.author: Bender

fields.text: I'm going to build my own theme park! With blackjack! And hookers! You know what- forget the park!
fields.author: Bender

fields.text: Blackmail's such an ugly word. I prefer extortion. The X makes it sound cool.
fields.author: Bender

fields.text: Valentine’s Day is coming up? Oh Crap, I forgot to get a girlfriend again!
fields.author: Fry

fields.text: Dammit Kif, where’s the little umbrella? That’s what makes it a scotch on the rocks!
fields.author: Zapp Brannnigan

fields.text: Finally, a uniform I’d be happy to be caught dead in!
fields.author: Amy

fields.text: I really ought to do something but I am already in my pyjamas.
